{"type": "article", "id": 29121, "title": "皮革相机包", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-04T22:55:22Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607042023587bC8KJQ64pwULBEW.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>一直都以其在意大利手工制作的皮革制品而闻名的英国品牌 <a href=\"https://www.hardgraft.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HARDGRAFT</a> 最近推出了一款名为 Pop Up 的相机包，专门为徕卡的 M、Q 系列以及其他尺寸相近的相机所设计。相机包采用了可折叠的设计，不使用的时候可以把它卷起当作日常用的手包或者是装进口袋里。Pop Up 除了选用来自意大利的植鞣皮革之外，还在可调节的肩带上融合了羊毛质地，毛料适当的厚度配合坚韧的皮革，让斜背变得更加舒适。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.hardgraft.com/products/popup-classic\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 348 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704202511wLCWnhXm5ibZqQAz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704202512wVNDt8CUX4dg9bWj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704202512qmIYUusb8loFWGcD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704202511lktMu2Z3K0XVWbcy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}